description: This skill generates a random fact about "30 Rock" an NBC Universal show. The user will say something along the lines of "Alexa, give me a thirty Rock fact" and Alexa will read aloud a fact inside the written skill. Alexa will output something along the lines of "Here's your thirty rock fact: 'followed by the fact'".
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask thirty Rockefeller trivia for a fact
Alexa, ask thirty Rockefeller trivia to give me a fact
name: Trivia for 30 Rock Fans
shortDescription: This skill will output a random fact about the NBC Universal show 30 Rock created by Tina Fey.
